Insider Activity


Individual




Robert Craig Owen



Mr. Robert C. Owen, CPA, is Chief Accounting Officer & Senior Vice President at Southwestern Energy Co. Mr. Owen was previously employed as Controller-Accounting Operations by Anadarko Petroleum Corp., a Principal by Arco Pipe Line Co., a Principal by Hilcorp Energy Co., and Manager-Business Assurance by PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP. He received his undergraduate degree from Texas A&M University.



