is available in 21 inter- mixable shades. Please refer to our color chart for the available hair color choices. Each box comes complete with everything you need to color your hair.>>>>>>





							 



Clear can be used alone to add shine to the hair or mixed with any of our 21 shades to create a colored gloss. If used alone, mix and apply for 15 minutes and enjoy the conditioning and shine benefits with no change in color. Mix with any of our 21 shades to refresh your color and achieve radiant, natural looking results.
							 





